"""
This package is created to store some useful scripts that are designed to run manually during development.

These scripts are intended to provide various utilities and helper functions that facilitate development tasks,
maintenance, data processing, and other ad-hoc operations. Unlike deployment scripts, which are executed
automatically during the deployment process, these utility scripts are meant to be run by developers as needed.

To use these scripts, run them by using relative path from the root of the project (e.g., `poetry run python src/external/scripts/<script_name>.py`).

Note: Make sure to review and understand the script's functionality before running it to avoid unintended consequences.
"""
